# ARSHIF Financial Hall — Certification Portal

A sovereign, local-first financial education portal built as a single-file vanilla HTML/CSS/JavaScript application. The portal is designed for learners, families, artists, entrepreneurs, homeschool programs, community builders, and self-directed adults who want a structured path through money literacy, consumer protection, budgeting, credit, debt, investing literacy, taxes, insurance, fraud prevention, ethics, and long-term stewardship.

> **Important boundary:** This project provides general financial education only. It is not individualized investment, tax, legal, insurance, benefits, accounting, or financial-adviser advice. The certificate generated by the portal is an ARSHIF Certificate of Completion, not an accredited degree, government license, securities license, tax-preparer credential, or professional financial-planning credential.

